room.title: 时代少年团
room.challenge_info: {"cid":"1646989394653197","cha_name":"时代少年团","desc":"时代少年团是由马嘉祺、丁程鑫、宋亚轩、刘耀文、张真源、严浩翔、贺峻霖七人组成的团体。\n2019年11月22日，发行单曲《全校通报》；11月23日，举行出道暨新歌首唱会 ，并发行单曲《无尽的冒险》 ；12月6日，获2020爱奇艺尖叫之夜年度潜力组合奖；12月8日，获TMEA腾讯音乐娱乐盛典年度新声代团体奖 我们主营家用经济代步车❗️
所有车辆保证无事故  水泡  火烧❗️

地址：成都市新都区宝光大道南段459号

{"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p1.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_ver
